This package builds a statically-linked (musl) binary, so the resulting .deb
has no shared-library dependencies and installs on any Debian/Ubuntu version.

Build all supported architectures in Docker (recommended):

$ ./build-deb-in-docker.sh

Or build a single target directly:

$ cargo install cargo-deb
$ rustup target add x86_64-unknown-linux-musl    # or aarch64-unknown-linux-musl
$ cargo deb --target x86_64-unknown-linux-musl
